title: Adorable 1 Bedroom / 1Bathroom Cabin.
posting_body: Adorable hilltop community just NE of Bastrop!
This 1 bedroom cabin is nearly new and includes one parking spot.
This nearly new unit features a covered porch, full bath with shower, kitchen with refrigerator and range/oven and a closet in the bedroom.
This is the perfect place for private living in a small quiet community!
Tenant must pay for trash & internet.
